## Master Flowchart - Complete Tax Lifecycle

This master flowchart shows how all tax scenarios interconnect from filing through collection and appeals.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Phase1["PHASE 1: FILING"]
        Start([Tax Year Ends]) --> Due[Return Due Date]
        Due --> Filed{Return<br/>Filed?}
        Filed -->|Yes| TimelyFiled{Filed by<br/>Due Date?}
        Filed -->|No| NoFile[NO RETURN FILED]
        TimelyFiled -->|Yes| OnTime[Timely Filed]
        TimelyFiled -->|No| Late[Late Filed]
    end

    subgraph Phase2["PHASE 2: PAYMENT"]
        OnTime --> TaxDue{Tax<br/>Owed?}
        Late --> TaxDue
        TaxDue -->|No| Refund[Refund Issued]
        TaxDue -->|Yes| Paid{Paid by<br/>Due Date?}
        Paid -->|Yes, Full| Complete([OBLIGATION COMPLETE])
        Paid -->|Yes, Partial| PartialPay[Partial Payment]
        Paid -->|No| NoPay[No Payment]
    end

    subgraph Phase3["PHASE 3: PENALTIES"]
        Late --> FTF[Failure to File Penalty<br/>5% per month - max 25%]
        PartialPay --> FTP[Failure to Pay Penalty<br/>0.5% per month - max 25%]
        NoPay --> FTP
        FTF --> FTP
        NoFile --> UnlimitedSOL[Unlimited SOL<br/>No Assessment Deadline]
    end

    subgraph Phase4["PHASE 4: ASSESSMENT"]
        FTP --> Assessment[IRS Assessment Made]
        UnlimitedSOL --> Assessment
        Assessment --> SOLCheck{Within<br/>SOL?}
        SOLCheck -->|3yr Normal| Assess3[Assessment Valid]
        SOLCheck -->|6yr >25% Omit| Assess6[Assessment Valid]
        SOLCheck -->|Expired| Barred[Assessment Barred]
    end

    subgraph Phase5["PHASE 5: COLLECTION"]
        Assess3 --> CP14[CP14: Balance Due Notice]
        Assess6 --> CP14
        CP14 --> Reminders[CP501/503/504 Reminders]
        Reminders --> Response{Taxpayer<br/>Responds?}
        Response -->|Yes| PayOptions[Payment Options]
        Response -->|No| Lien[Federal Tax Lien Filed]
        Lien --> FinalNotice[Final Notice:<br/>Intent to Levy]
        FinalNotice --> CDP{CDP Hearing<br/>Requested?}
        CDP -->|Yes| CDPHearing[CDP Hearing<br/>Collection Suspended]
        CDP -->|No| Levy[LEVY ACTION]
    end

    subgraph Phase6["PHASE 6: RESOLUTION"]
        PayOptions --> FullPay[Full Payment]
        PayOptions --> IA[Installment Agreement]
        PayOptions --> OIC[Offer in Compromise]
        PayOptions --> CNC[Currently Not Collectible]
        FullPay --> Resolved([CASE CLOSED])
        IA --> Resolved
        OIC --> Resolved
        CDPHearing --> CDPOutcome{CDP<br/>Outcome}
        CDPOutcome -->|Favorable| Released[Lien/Levy Released]
        CDPOutcome -->|Unfavorable| TaxCourtAppeal[Appeal to Tax Court]
    end

    subgraph Phase7["PHASE 7: AUDIT PATH"]
        Assessment -.->|IRS Selects| Audit[Examination/Audit]
        Audit --> AuditResult{Audit<br/>Result}
        AuditResult -->|No Change| AuditClosed([Case Closed])
        AuditResult -->|Changes| ThirtyDay[30-Day Letter]
        ThirtyDay --> Agree{Taxpayer<br/>Agrees?}
        Agree -->|Yes| PayDeficiency[Pay Deficiency]
        Agree -->|No| NinetyDay[90-Day Letter<br/>Notice of Deficiency]
        NinetyDay --> TaxCourt{Petition<br/>Tax Court?}
        TaxCourt -->|Yes, 90 days| USTC[U.S. Tax Court]
        TaxCourt -->|No| FinalAssess[Assessment Final]
    end
```

