## 2. Penalty Assessment Flowchart

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Determine["DETERMINE PENALTY TYPE"]
        Start[Tax Due but Not Paid] --> Filed{Return<br/>Filed?}
        Filed -->|No| FTF[Failure to File Penalty]
        Filed -->|Yes| CheckPay{Full Payment<br/>by Due Date?}
        CheckPay -->|No| FTP[Failure to Pay Penalty]
        CheckPay -->|Yes| NoPenalty([No Penalty])
    end

    subgraph FTFCalc["FAILURE TO FILE PENALTY"]
        FTF --> FTFRate[5% of unpaid tax<br/>per month or partial month]
        FTFRate --> FTFMax[Maximum: 25%<br/>5 months]
        FTFMax --> FTFMin{Return 60+<br/>days late?}
        FTFMin -->|Yes| MinPenalty[Minimum Penalty:<br/>Lesser of $510 or<br/>100% of tax due]
        FTFMin -->|No| NoMin[Standard Calculation]
    end

    subgraph FTPCalc["FAILURE TO PAY PENALTY"]
        FTP --> FTPRate[0.5% of unpaid tax<br/>per month or partial month]
        FTPRate --> FTPMax[Maximum: 25%<br/>50 months]
        FTPMax --> LevyIssued{Levy Notice<br/>Issued?}
        LevyIssued -->|Yes| Increase[Increases to 1%<br/>per month]
        LevyIssued -->|No| Standard[Remains 0.5%]
    end

    subgraph Combined["COMBINED PENALTIES"]
        FTFCalc --> Both{Both Penalties<br/>Apply?}
        FTPCalc --> Both
        Both -->|Yes| Reduction[FTF Reduced to 4.5%<br/>FTF 4.5% + FTP 0.5% = 5% total per month]
        Both -->|No| Single[Single Penalty Applies]
        Reduction --> MaxCombined[Maximum Combined:<br/>47.5% total<br/>25% FTF + 22.5% FTP for months 1-5<br/>then 0.5% FTP continues]
    end

    subgraph Interest["INTEREST CALCULATION"]
        MaxCombined --> InterestCalc[Interest: Federal Short-Term Rate + 3%]
        Single --> InterestCalc
        InterestCalc --> Compound[Compounded Daily<br/>Runs from Due Date until Paid]
    end

    subgraph Special["SPECIAL PENALTIES"]
        Accuracy[Accuracy-Related Penalty<br/>20% of underpayment]
        Fraud[Civil Fraud Penalty<br/>75% of underpayment]
        Accuracy --> Negligence[Negligence or<br/>Substantial Understatement]
        Fraud --> Replace[Replaces Accuracy Penalty<br/>Does NOT stack]
    end
```

